Common.LocationDescription.Common.Text:
Prominently located along the Magnificent Mile, 737 North Michigan is only steps from distinguished hotels, award-winning restaurants, world-famous stores, luxury spas, health and fitness facilities and the areas expanding medical campus.
737 North Michigans desirable location is easily accessible and provides its tenants employees and guests with convenient commute options. Vehicular traffic benefits from the buildings 435 car underground parking garage as well as easy access to and from I-90/94 and Lake Shore Drive. Numerous CTA bus routes along Michigan Avenue and the CTA Red Line stop on Chicago Avenue, make traveling to and from 737 North Michigan a breeze with public transportation as well.

Common.LongDescription.Common.Text:
Welcome to 737 North Michigan, a prestigious corporate environment, exemplifying style and sophistication. Designed by Skidmore Owings and Merrill with a uniquely curved exterior, 737 North Michigan is an eye-catching architectural addition to the Magnificent Mile in Chicago. With beautiful clad granite panels that taper as they ascend and floor to ceiling windows providing dramatic city views the structural design is both stunning and brilliant.
 

Consisting of 335,000 square feet of Class A office space, Neiman Marcus, luxury condominiums and a 435 car underground parking facility, 737 North Michigan caters to a diverse, high-profile audience. A recently renovated artistically inspired lobby with striking limestone floors, handsome eucalyptus wood veneered panels, and skillfully designed energy efficient lighting provides a welcoming arrival for office tenants and visitors. Superior access to distinguished hotels, luxurious spas, award-winning restaurants, and world famous stores and healthcare facilities offer convenience and office elegance on the Avenue.
